Package structures.arrays

Class ArrayOfInt

  • java.lang.Object
    • structures.arrays.ArrayOfInt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>, Allocable, Freeable
    public class ArrayOfInt
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Integer>, Allocable
    Class to symbolize an array of int.
    Similar to the SuccessionOf class, this one is specifically for the primitive type int. Works similarly.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      (package private) static class  ArrayOfInt.Allocator
      The allocator that is in charge of the SuccessionOfInt type.
      When not specified, the allocator has an initial capacity of 16.
